Ex-BP CEO Browne May Chair National Grid, Sunday Times Reports

-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 
2011-05-15T07:39:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-15/ex-bp-ceo-browne-may-chair-national-grid-sunday-times-reports.html
John Browne , the former  BP Plc (BP/)  chief
executive officer, is one of two candidates to replace John Parker as chairman of the U.K.’s  National Grid Plc (NG/) , the Sunday
Times reported.  Ken Harvey, National Grid’s senior independent director who
leads the search for the chairman, will update the board on his
progress this week, the newspaper said, without citing anyone.
Parker’s replacement is likely to be announced at the company’s
annual meeting in July, according to the Sunday Times.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Ermakova in London at 
 mermakova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
